Changes introduced in the recent TVT versions
---------------------------------------------

3.0.2
----- <March 22 2004>

 * A support for wild cards added to tvt.extendedrules.
 * New features to tvt.illux.
 * A bug in tvt.parallel fixed that produced results bigger than necessary
   when using stubborn sets.

3.0.1
----- <May 20 2003>

 * An erroneus handling of livelock reject proposition in tvt.parallel
   fixed.
 * tvt.CFFDcompare script fixed (*nix only).
 * A bug in handling header promises of LSTS files fixed.
